WEBVTT

00:02.383 --> 00:05.163
No. No -
I should've said it well before now.

00:05.197 --> 00:06.395
I love you.

00:06.397 --> 00:09.515
James attempted suicide on the ship
the night before we docked.

00:09.517 --> 00:10.715
No.

00:10.717 --> 00:12.035
He's looking for answers.

00:12.037 --> 00:14.115
You have to find a story
he can believe.

00:14.117 --> 00:16.235
The best lie is
a version of the truth.

00:16.236 --> 00:19.515
Before we got married,
I was in love with someone.

00:19.517 --> 00:23.235
All this time
I... I thought it was me!

00:23.237 --> 00:24.675
I want you at the hospital.

00:24.677 --> 00:26.195
And I'll fight to keep you there.

00:26.197 --> 00:28.115
Enough to make her your enemy too?

00:28.117 --> 00:29.395
She saved his life!

00:29.397 --> 00:30.835
And now she threatens to ruin it.

00:30.837 --> 00:32.795
And you repay her
by running her out of town?

00:32.797 --> 00:34.315
I don't want it to come between us.

00:34.317 --> 00:37.997
But it's a risk you're clearly
prepared to take. Go on - get out.

